{"tid":1637004,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"東涌友）表白勇武）港島區被收工）","createTime":"2019-10-08T00:56:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T00:56:12.000Z","uid":311522,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"597e6b1b99eb32659864b8e4702617aabc86c57d","tid":1637004,"uid":311522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T00:56:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k6eRpJh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk6eRpJh.jpg&h=1f1ffa1c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>多謝勇武</strong></span><br />\n但希望你地帶返文具先裝修<br />\n保障返自己安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n作為一個曾經返地產的香港人嚟講<br />\n千祈咪睇少東涌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無論去機場定去澳門珠海<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">東涌條路係必經既</span></span><br />\n党铁一停左就淨返路面去青馬<br />\n一炒車就塞到2046<br />\n東涌除左新移民之外<br />\n仲有好多外國人同埋返港島區既工作人士<br />\n東涌租金比港島最少平一半<br />\n東涌綫平時一線到香港<br />\n佢地轉一站就港島<br />\n無党铁就要塞車返工<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家都知港島區好重要<br />\n如果返唔到工你地話個影響有幾多呢？"}]}